            <title>[AVRO-1717] [Github] Support for optional fields when converting json to avro</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1717</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently there is an issue when we want to convert json object to avro using schema that allows optional fields (fields of type &apos;null&apos;). When json object does not explicitly have such field with &apos;null&apos; value then is treated as not conforming to schema. I added few test cases that illustrate this problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;PR: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/avro/pull/47&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/avro/pull/47&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
