            <title>[AVRO-1718] Reuse types on Protocol</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1718</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On version 1.7.6 was added a new feature to import and reuse schemas in other schema files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This feature works fine on Schema, but it is great if this feature works on Protocol, because you can write the Schema files and use on Protocol files without declare again the types&lt;/p&gt;</description>
